To have an orb move in the direction the player is facing we 
would set the direction of the orb. In the player class theirs
a variable called direction then set the players direction to
the direction of the orb. Set up a public void getDirection in 
the player class then continue to establish rules and speed for
the ball in the game class. Setting up direction when the space 
key is pressed of the last arrow key that is pressed.
